column1: The p8 gene was cloned in human, rat, mouse, and Xenopus laevis [ 1, 4 - 6], conceptually translated from the Drosophila melanogaster genome or deduced from EST libraries ( Bos taurus, Xenopus tropicalis, Zebrafish, Orzzias latipes, Bombyx mori and Paralichthys olivaceous).
